{"type":"message","id":"df7bbb0e","parentId":"2e15ab09","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:35:33.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"不是墨墨，我是 Aight（艾特）——你的另一个 AI 助手。🙂\n\n墨墨是另一个独立的 agent，你有需要可以直接 @墨墨 叫她。\n\n我们现在在我的工作区里，刚才读取了记忆文件，发现这是一个全新的工作区，还没有初始化。你想现在给我起个名字、定义一下我的风格吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773578130492}}
